snippet.textDisplay: James I highly recommend using the elf hydrating moisturizer because after using it for a few weeks, it actually balanced my skin really well from oiliness. I have combo skin (oily-normal and a few dry patches) and when I would use it before makeup, it didn’t really mess up my foundation in my t-zone area or on the dry patches on my face. I get that it may not work well on similar skin types but I highly recommend it and I hope you give it a try :)
